### User get
GET {{HostAddress}}/user/getuser
Accept: application/json



### Create Role
POST {{HostAddress}}/role
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
{
  "Name": "User",
  "IsSystemRole": true,
  "SystemName" : "Users",
  "Active": true
}

### Get Roles
GET {{HostAddress}}/role
Accept: application/json

### Get Role by system name
GET {{HostAddress}}/role/Users
Accept: application/json

